#: ../../source/api/appearance.md:1
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Appearance"

#: ../../source/api/appearance.md:3
msgid "`Appearance` is the parent class of `Background` and `Costume`."
msgstr "`Appearance` ist die Basisklasse von `Background` und `Costume`."

#: ../../source/api/appearance.md:5
msgid ""
"Backgrounds and costumes are appearances as well, so they inherit all "
"attributes and methods defined in this class."
msgstr ""
"Backgrounds und Costumes sind ebenfalls Appearances und erben daher alle in "
"dieser Klasse definierten Attribute und Methoden."

#: ../../source/api/appearance.md:8
msgid "API Reference"
msgstr "API-Referenz"

#: miniworlds.appearances.appearance.Appearance:1 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "Base class for actor costumes and world backgrounds."
msgstr "Basisklasse von Actorkostümen und Welt-Hintergründen"

#: miniworlds.appearances.appearance.Appearance:3 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`Appearance` is the parent class of both `Costume` and `Background`. You "
"normally access it through `actor.costume` or `world.background`."
msgstr "`Appearance` ist die Basisklasse von `Background` und `Costume`."

